       fhir:comment [ fhir:v "The individual's gender identity is populated in the `extension:value.value[x]` of the [Individual Gender Identity](http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/individual-genderIdentity) extension and shall contain one of the codes from the [Gender Identity Response](https://healthterminologies.gov.au/fhir/ValueSet/gender-identity-response-1) value set if any of the codes within the value set can apply.\n\nSee [Australian Bureau of Statics (ABS) Standard for Sex, Gender, Variations of Sex Characteristics and Sexual Orientation Variables, 2020](https://www.abs.gov.au/statistics/standards/standard-sex-gender-variations-sex-characteristics-and-sexual-orientation-variables/latest-release#gender) for further materials." ] ;
